<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
        href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <title>LogRequest</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <br />
                <div class="jumbotron" style="background: #331880;">
                    <h4 class="text-white">Log Request for HelpDesk solutions!</h4>
                    <h2 class="text-white">Envio de arquivos de logs!</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="alert alert-danger mt-3">
                    Pasta de logs fica localizada dentro da pasta de instalação da
                    solução.
                    <br>
                    <b>Ex: 'C:\Program Files\Ferramenta\Logs', '/var/logs/nginx'</b>.
                    <br>
                    <br /> Se houver mais de um arquivo de log, pastas ou imagens de erro como
                    screenshots.
                    <br>
                    compacte-os no formato zip ou 7z. e anexe!.
                </p>
                <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form-group"
                    id="uploadForm">
                    <div>
                        <label for="inpFile" class="form-label">Anexo de arquivo <b>zip ou
                                7z</b></label>
                        <input class="form-control form-control" id="inpFile" type="file"
                            name="file" required>
                        <!-- <br>
                        <label for="inpFileImage" class="form-label">Anexe até 10 arquivos e <b>imagens</b> como
                            Screenshots, Erros, Etc...</label>
                        <input class="form-control form-control" id="inpFileImage" type="file"
                            name="fImagens" multiple> -->
                        <button style="background: #262624; border: none;" type="submit"
                            class="mt-3 btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg">Enviar</button>
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <div class="progress" id="progressBar" style="height: 30px;">
                        <div id="progress-bar-id" class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated"
                            role="progressbar" style="width: 0%" aria-valuenow="25"
                            aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"><span style="font-weight: bold;"
                                id="progress-text"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="static/js/upload_file.js"></script>

</body>

</html>